          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/54656100/">陈阿奇</a>
            <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/3963402928">2023-10-15 19:07:04</a>
          <span class="comment-location">上海</span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">这部作品诠释了经典，也成了经典。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1868698/?comment_id=3963402928"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
